      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHICKEN FISH (7) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 27.88 beating Just A Joker. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. ALL ABOUT COAL (2) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant seventh (28.14) in a Grade 5 over 488m at this track. Can do much better this time. IMPRESS DORY (4) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when eighth at Cannington over 601m behind Take My Advice (35.89) in a Grade 5. Has ability and can measure up. KENTISH LASS (8) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
